Class AQLBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.knaw.huygens.antioch.antlr.AQLBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AQLListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class AQLBaseListener
extends Object
implements AQLListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of AQLListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
